item.title: Peter Moore Looks Back: An Interview Celebrating the Xbox 360's 20th Anniversary
item.description: In this conversation, Peter Moore reflects on his journey from Sega to Xbox, discussing pivotal moments in the gaming industry, including the launch of the Xbox 360 and the Zero Hour event. He shares insights on key partnerships, the challenges faced in the Japanese market, and the strategic decisions that shaped the Xbox brand. Moore emphasizes the importance of putting gamers first and the evolution of the industry towards a multi-platform strategy... Feed: https://audioboom.com/channels/4949308.rss
